{"type":"message","id":"6bd2acaf","parentId":"06310fe1","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:56:59.035Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see clearly what happened. The evolver ran and immediately FAILED with constraints violations:\n\n1. **HARD CAP BREACH**: 155 files / 33378 lines exceeds system limit (60 files / 20000 lines)\n2. **critical_path_modified**: AGENTS.md, MEMORY.md, TOOLS.md\n3. **CRITICAL_FILE_DELETED**: AGENTS.md, MEMORY.md, TOOLS.md\n4. **validation_failed**: test suite exited with code 1\n\nThe evolver tried to modify/rewrite/delete the core agent files (AGENTS.md, MEMORY.md, TOOLS.md) which are critical files - this triggered HARD CAP and constraint violations and it failed.\n\n\nI'm realizing this was a full cycle run of the evolver, and it looks like the previous session already had partial changes applied. The \"files changed\" count of 155 with equal lines added and removed suggests files were replaced rather than cleanly modified. The critical files got deleted or modified in the process, and the test suite validation failed as a result.\n","thinkingSignature":"d6b772838cb491a59805860f67327503316c6470c3993f7b60ee6d75a4eda2e4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xq11141h3mfn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/halei/workspace-tts/AGENTS.md /home/halei/workspace-tts/MEMORY.md /home/halei/workspace-tts/TOOLS.md 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xq11141h3mfn_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git -C /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace status --short 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":877,"output":328,"cacheRead":90304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91509,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778849796439,"responseId":"06564b05d1c190672f01a6f4fd836ee5"}}
