{"type":"message","id":"c908d808","parentId":"0c54fd5c","timestamp":"2026-05-15T12:57:29.876Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - the last_run now shows the latest run happened at 2026-05-15T12:56:36.234Z (today!), gene is `gene_gep_repair_from_errors` with outcome still not recorded.\n\nThis confirms that capability-evolver did run today (just now) and is actively working. The issue is that the previous run (the one I triggered manually) tried to modify 155 files and failed validation because it hit HARD CAP BREACH.\n\nThe system correctly rejected the mutation. This means evolver IS working - it detected a signal, tried a mutation, failed validation, and rolled back. That's the correct behavior.\n\n\nI should wrap this up by confirming the system operated as intended today, providing a summary of what happened, and noting whether there are any follow-up actions worth considering.\n","thinkingSignature":"b19fbaeead9af385b51586de30eb0155301b4932b225de072d67fb3666260c72"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**capability-evolver 在工作**，刚才我手动触发了，今天已经跑了两次：\n\n**第一次运行（刚运行）：**\n- 检测到信号：`user_feature_request` + `tool_bypass` + `high_failure_ratio`\n- 基因：`gene_gep_innovate_from_opportunity`\n- **结果：失败**\n- 原因：**HARD CAP BREACH** — 155 文件 / 33378 行，超过了系统限制（60 文件 / 20000 行）\n- 触碰了禁止路径：AGENTS.md、MEMORY.md、TOOLS.md\n- 测试套件也 FAIL 了\n- **结论：触发器被正确拒绝，Rollback 生效 ✅**\n\n**第二次运行（solidify 阶段）：**\n- 切换到了 `gene_gep_repair_from_errors`（修复基因）\n- 同样是失败（验证不通过）\n- 当前状态：`outcome_recorded: null`，还没完成记录\n\n**问题诊断：**\ncapability-evolver 在今天早上 8 点之后试图做一次大规模演化——根据你当时问\"能扫描到现在有多少agent\"这个信号，触发了一个创新突变。但它的改动范围太大（155 文件），直接被硬性限制拦下来了。Rollback 也正确执行了，所以文件没真被改坏。\n\n**它需要什么才能正常工作？**\n1. 它的改动范围太大了，当前设置对多 Agent 环境来说太激进\n2. 信号解析有问题——把\"扫描agent\"误判为\"需要创新\"\n3. 工作空间文件不在它的基线里，导致 baseline 检测失效\n\n要我调整它的策略配置（比如把 `EVOLVE_STRATEGY` 改成 `harden`），或者看看具体是哪个信号触发的误判？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":228,"output":521,"cac