{"type":"message","id":"d6985da0","parentId":"8e62fc89","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:06:20.865Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture. The evolver ran twice today and both times failed because the signal from dreaming (`user_feature_request:给自己取个名字...`) keeps getting picked up, causing it to try to create new agents/capabilities that it shouldn't.\n\nThe core issue: the evolver keeps detecting this dreaming output as a `user_feature_request` signal, triggering `gene_gep_innovate_from_opportunity`, which tries to create 155 files (a new agent/capability), which is way over the limit.\n\nNow let me set up a cron job and configure the evolver properly.\n","thinkingSignature":"476e17d0a5e41baf807bd04d66151eaeebf40cd95ff84132c71814bde9fbe8ea"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n问题根源找到了 — capability-evolver 被 `dreaming` 里残留的信号卡住了。梦境输出里有一句\"给自己取个名字\"，被误判为 `user_feature_request`，触发了创新基因要创建新 Agent，覆盖 155 文件直接爆表。\n\n现在给它设 cron 定时任务 + 切 `harden` 策略：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g3hxuylbyqot_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu"},"name":"capability-evolver-daily","payload":{"allowUnsafeExternalContent":false,"kind":"agentTurn","message":"你是一个本地进化引擎。运行以下命令：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/capability-evolver && EVOLVE_STRATEGY=harden node index.js run 2>&1 | tail -20\n```\n\n如果输出包含「SOLIDIFY REQUIRED」或成功完成，将结果追加写入 `memory/evolution/evolution_narrative.md`。\n\n如果发现 155 files 或「给自己取个名字」这个信号，返回 HEARTBEAT_OK（不要运行 evolver）。\n\n完成后返回运行结果摘要（基因名、outcome、信号数量）。","model":"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7","timeoutSeconds":300},"schedule":{"expr":"0 9 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated"}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":410,"output":467,"cacheRead":137536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138413,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopRea