{"type":"message","id":"08805d07","parentId":"ffef5547","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:11:25.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The signal is still there because the memory_graph.jsonl (which is the memory graph database) still contains that session content as a node. So renaming the corpus file doesn't help - the signal is already baked into the memory_graph.jsonl.\n\nI need a different approach: clean the memory_graph.jsonl or add that signal to the exclusion list. \n\nActually, let me look at how the signals are detected. The \"user_feature_request\" signal with the full Chinese text about \"给自己取个名字\" is coming from a recent session (the one where you were doing Chinese translation of files). This session is still in the session logs.\n\nLet me try a different approach - let me reset the evolver completely by:\n","thinkingSignature":"e2238e2c729c10f2d87bce8171590ec4ae12abc97b44875da5b4f4d0d9fa9b5f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lsezpywkkojv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 清理 memory_graph 中的问题信号记录，重置 evolver 状态\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/capability-evolver\n\n# 重置 evolution_solidify_state 到初始状态（清除 last_run）\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\n\npath = 'memory/evolution/evolution_solidify_state.json'\nwith open(path) as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\n\n# 清除 last_run - 强制重新开始\nd.pop('last_run', None)\nd['cycleId'] = '0002'\n\nwith open(path, 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\nprint('Cleared last_run. cycleId:', d['cycleId'])\n\"\n\n# 重命名 memory_graph（它是信号来源）\nif [ -f memory/evolution/memory_graph.jsonl ]; then\n    ts=$(date +%Y%m%d%H%M%S)\n    cp memory/evolution/memory_graph.jsonl \"memory/evolution/memory_graph.jsonl.bak$ts\"\n    # 只保留前100行（清除旧信号）\n    head -100 memory/evolution/memory_graph.jsonl > memory/evolution/memory_graph.jsonl.tmp && mv memory/evolution/memory_graph.jsonl.tmp memory/evolution/memory_graph.jsonl\n    echo \"memory_graph trimmed. New size: $(wc -l < memory/evolution/memory_graph.jsonl) lines\"\nfi"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":719,"output":470,"cacheRead":142656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143845,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778850666540,"responseId":"06564e6bee3ffded7175d0f2043a26b6"}}
