{"type":"message","id":"364e21ed","parentId":"dcc53db9","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:12:26.481Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, the cron job is set up. Let me summarize everything to the user now.The key issue is that evolver is picking up an old signal from a session corpus file that contains \"给自己取个名字\" (a dream diary entry). This is causing it to fail with HARD CAP BREACH because the evolver interprets this as a user feature request and tries to generate 155 files.\n\nThe cron is set up. The signal issue is a known bug that we're working around by trimming the memory_graph.\n\nNow let me report everything to the user clearly.\n","thinkingSignature":"05cd680ad6c9dbe9b17cfca53d10a31aaff837f20b6424ceb3597cb24574d458"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定了 🎉\n\n**进度总结：**\n\n✅ **定时任务已设置** — 每天早上 9:00 自动运行 `capability-evolver`\n- cron job id: `6a3ece23-2e6a-493c-940c-0df4ca593a67`\n- 每天 Asia/Shanghai 9:00 执行\n- 用 `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=harden` 策略（减少激进突变）\n- 完成后会发飞书通知\n\n✅ **问题信号已隔离** — 导致 evolver 卡死的\"给自己取个名字\"那个 session corpus 文件已跳过\n\n⚠️ **一个已知 Bug** — evolver 会错误地把 dreaming session 中的文字当成 `user_feature_request` 信号。清理了相关文件后，目前 memory_graph 已缩减到 39 行。\n\n**当前 evolver 状态：**\n- 策略：harden（安全优先，不容易触发大规模改动）\n- 触发基因：`gene_gep_repair_from_errors`（修复错误，不是创新）\n- 定时：每天 9:00 自动跑\n- 通知：跑完结果发飞书\n\n如果明天 9 点跑完有结果会通知你，你可以看看它到底有没有做出有用的改变。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":258,"output":373,"cacheRead":144384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145015,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778850726309,"responseId":"06564ea7f6c91bf1dee80d32774d4bf3"}}
