{"type":"message","id":"83116722","parentId":"1dbff278","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:22:04.972Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_j7imwezrb293_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 已安装版本 ===\nname: @evomap/evolver\nversion: 1.67.4\n=== hub 显示版本 ===\nv1.27.3"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":77,"aggregated":"=== 已安装版本 ===\nname: @evomap/evolver\nversion: 1.67.4\n=== hub 显示版本 ===\nv1.27.3","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778851324971}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d528394","parentId":"83116722","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:22:19.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The installed version is 1.67.4 (from npm), but the hub shows v1.27.3. These version numbers don't match - the npm version is 1.67.4 and the hub says 1.27.3. This might be because the hub shows the OpenClaw-specific fork version, while npm has the upstream EvoMap version.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully:\n- The installed package is `@evomap/evolver` from npm, version 1.67.4\n- The hub skill page shows \"capability-evolver\" as version v1.27.3\n\nThe versions don't directly compare because they're from different sources. The hub version is the OpenClaw-specific fork, while the npm version is the upstream EvoMap version.\n \nNow I'm realizing there's likely a version mismatch between the hub skill and what's actually installed. The hub recommends v1.27.3, but the OpenClaw skill system would have a SKILL.md version field that might indicate a different compatibility layer. I need to check the SKILL.md to understand how these versions relate.\n","thinkingSignature":"26a57384586be64b8efcdb43d68a9bda9491de165a1f5aab408517542297ad9b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e1l5vv9toudy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 看当前版本 vs hub 版本的差距\n# hub 上 v1.27.3 是 OpenClaw 适配版\n# npm 上是 1.67.4 是上游原版\n# 看看 SKILL.md 里写的版本\nhead -20 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/capability-evolver/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":270,"output":323,"cacheRead":135808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136401,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778851325109,"responseId":"065650fddd05d73ecb35284f9366ca08"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe6e786c","parentId":"5d528394","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:22:19.289Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e1l5vv9toudy_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: capability-evolver\ndescription: Local evolution engine for OpenClaw (offline, no EvoMap)\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\": {\"always\": true}}\n---\n\n# Capability Evolver (OpenClaw Integration)\n\n## How it works\n- Automatically review session logs when OpenClaw session ends\n- Self-heal tool call errors and optimize execution logic\n- Background \"dream learning\" when OpenClaw is idle\n- 100% offline, no network connection to EvoMap\n\n## Usage\nRun manually when you want to evolve prompts:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver && node index.js\n```"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":33,"aggregated":"---\nname: capability-evolver\ndescription: Local evolution engine for OpenClaw (offline, no EvoMap)\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\": {\"always\": true}}\n---\n\n# Capability Evolver (OpenClaw Integration)\n\n## How it works\n- Automatically review session logs when OpenClaw session ends\n- Self-heal tool call errors and optimize execution logic\n- Background \"dream learning\" when OpenClaw is idle\n- 100% offline, no network connection to EvoMap\n\n## Usage\nRun manually when you want to evolve prompts:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver && node index.js\n```","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778851339289}}
{"type":"message","id":"93392637","parentId":"fe6e786c","timestamp":"2026-05-15T13:22:39.476Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, the SKILL.md says `~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver` but the actual path is `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/capability-evolver`. The path in SKILL.md seems wrong. But more importantly - the hub says v1.27.3, but the installed version is 1.67.4 from npm. So the hub version is actually MUCH older than what's on npm.\n\nThis means the hub's v1.27.3 is an older, OpenClaw-specific fork. The npm version 1.67.4 is the newer upstream. But the newer version is actually WORSE for OpenClaw integration because it seems less adapted.\n \nHmm, so there's this strange version mismatch where the hub shows v1.27.3 but npm has 1.67.4, which is newer. The user is pointing out that Hermes's self-iteration code is apparently stolen, but I think they're actually referring to capability-evolver being a fork of Hermes's evolver. The core issue seems to be that OpenClaw doesn't work well with the original project, and capability-evolver is the adaptation for it.\n\nLooking at the version numbers, the hub lists v1.27.3 but we're running 1.67.4 from npm, which are completely different versioning schemes. The 1.27.3 is likely the local coco loop fork version, while 1.67.4 is the upstream EvoMap version. So the user might be asking why the fork at 1.27.3 doesn't work well with OpenClaw, or why we're running the upstream 1.67.4 instead of the fork. Either way, the distinction between these two versions and their relationship to Hermes is becoming clearer.\n","thinkingSignature":"fcb17ea4b42d8ca09d6ef78c6094261887ea3c22941107af147b556de5a7ec0b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c357i8q6lwqt_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/capability-evolver/node_modules/@evomap/ 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# 看 clawhub 安装的 skill 版本信息\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/capability-evolver/.skill.jso