{"type":"message","id":"58f37a3e","parentId":"524fc057","timestamp":"2026-05-15T14:04:02.123Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The lark-cli updated to 1.0.32 successfully! And the auth status shows it's working. Let me give the user a quick summary.","thinkingSignature":"6b925a796af403f6cce1ed6a46c4a29e357578dc03ea0669c84decbb21f1b32d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定了 ✅\n\n**lark-cli 更新完成：**\n- 旧版本：1.0.27\n- 新版本：**1.0.32**\n- 认证状态：正常（`identity: \"bot\"`）\n\n认证没断，更新后直接能用。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114,"output":90,"cacheRead":129856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130060,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778853837281,"responseId":"06565acd38813c1484f3ce3268880cb4"}}
